metadata.name: equality and fairness Open Editions
metadata.description:
the rights of the LGBTQ+ community are crucial for creating a more equal and accepting society.  
LGBTQ+ rights also have a positive impact on the mental health and well-being of those who identify as part of the community.  
Advocating for LGBTQ+ rights helps to break down harmful stereotypes and promotes a more nuanced understanding of this diverse group of people.  
https://app.manifold.xyz/c/LGBTQ
